Praet reveals why he turned down Arsenal<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I had three or four really good options,&rdquo; Praet told the Guardian. &ldquo;We went to visit Arsenal, Lille, Ajax and Anderlecht. Arsenal would have been a really nice step and I could earn a lot more money there than in Anderlecht, but at that moment my education was not finished and that was really important for me &ndash; there was no insurance that I would become a good football player.&rdquo;
